205
00:07:09,229 --> 00:07:11,839
But if the VIP money stops rolling through,

206
00:07:11,839 --> 00:07:13,040
it will be pretty obvious t

207
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:16,340
hat the entire system is a corrupt sham—

208
00:07:16,340 --> 00:07:19,520
and that would be a huge embarrassment for
the Party.

209
00:07:19,520 --> 00:07:22,520
So the CCP is between a rock and a hard place.

210
00:07:22,520 --> 00:07:24,539
It’s like when you fall into a pit,

211
00:07:24,539 --> 00:07:26,681
